#####################################################################
# This example demonstrates various ways to create and access
# ID attribute using libabac api
# and use query to show that it is indeed in the db  

case 1: make attribute rule
        writing attribute cert file
        load attribute cert

case 2: make attribute rule
        load attribute

case 3: make attribute rule  -- not in RT0
        retrieve attribute cert chunk
        make new attribute with cert chunk
        load new attribute

case 4: make attribute rule
        retrieve attribute cert chunk
        load attribute cert chunk directly into context


